issue.title: Rename to Stega and Update README / Docs
issue.body:
Now that this is moving past 36 hour hackathon mode, we should rename the project and try and add some documentation.

1.  A disclaimer. This is still a big WIP and we don't offer any guarantees about its functionality.
2. Docs. The project is pretty simple to use at the moment, but could use some small comments on how to use it. In particular: what command to start the server with and how to choose public and private keys.
